       _r_._s_t_a_t_s calculates the area present in each of the categories of  user-
       selected  raster  map  layer(s).  Area statistics are given in units of
       square meters and/or cell counts. This analysis uses the  current  geo-
       graphic  region and mask settings.  Output can be sent to a file in the
       user's current working directory.


